# Page & Component Patterns

## Server Page Structure (list pages)
```
<div className="p-6 space-y-6">
  {/* Header */}
  <div className="flex items-center justify-between">
    <div>
      <h1 className="text-2xl font-bold">Title</h1>
      <p className="text-sm text-muted-foreground mt-1">Subtitle</p>
    </div>
    {canEdit && <Button asChild><Link href="...">Action</Link></Button>}
  </div>
  {/* StatCards grid */}
  <div className="grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">...</div>
  {/* Table or empty state */}
</div>
```

## Empty State Pattern
```
<div className="rounded-md border p-8 text-center">
  <Icon className="mx-auto h-10 w-10 text-muted-foreground/50" />
  <p className="mt-3 text-sm text-muted-foreground">Guidance text</p>
  <Button asChild variant="outline" size="sm" className="mt-4">
    <Link href="...">CTA</Link>
  </Button>
</div>
```

## Client Component Pattern
- Use `useTransition` + `sonner` toast for async actions.
- `isPending` disables buttons with "Action…" text.
- CSV exports: blob → URL.createObjectURL → click → revoke.

## Imports to prefer
- `StatCard` from `@/components/stat-card`
- `Badge` from `@/components/ui/badge`
- `Table/*` from `@/components/ui/table`
- `Card/*` from `@/components/ui/card`
- `Button` from `@/components/ui/button`
- Icons from `lucide-react`
- Toast from `sonner`
